{"name": "Swedish Language", "id": 256, "content": "<p>From documents:</p>\n\n<p>H&auml;r kommer en sammanst&auml;llning <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/saamman-stalnin(g)/</span> &ouml;ver <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/a&#39;ver/</span> den information <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/infirma&#39;-hoon/</span> som har h&auml;mtat <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/haem&#39;tath/</span> om dig. [Here&#39;s the summary of the information that has been collected about you]</p>\n\n<p>i skickar alltid <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/i-k(h)wi-gar-alti/</span> en kopia till dig s&aring; du vet <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/veut/</span> vilken information vi har l&auml;mnat ut om dig<span style=\"color:#f39c12;\"> /vi-a-lamna-tu-tom-de&#39;/</span>. [i always send you a copy so you know what information we have disclosed about you.]</p>\n\n<p>Det &auml;r vi skyldiga <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/k(h)wildigau/</span>&nbsp; enligt Kreditupplysningslagen <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/K(h)rdit-uplisning-slaugen/</span>. [We owe that under the Credit Reporting Act.]</p>\n\n<p>Har du fr&aring;gor kring det som st&aring;r h&auml;r i brevet hittar du de flesta <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/festa/</span> svaren p&aring; uc.se/upplysningskopian [If you have questions about what is written here in the letter, you will find most of the answers on uc.se/upplysningskopian]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://interlinearbooks.com/literature/swedish/reader/karlek-och-politik\" target=\"_blank\">Karlek <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/Charlec/</span> och Politik</a> (Love and Politics)</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold\">F&ouml;rsta scenen. <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">(First Scene)</span></span></p>\n\n<p>(En bondstuga. Elsa sitter vid bordet <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/-oo-/</span> och l&auml;ser ett brev <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/breuhv/</span>. Anna kommer in, s&auml;tter sig <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/say/</span> p&aring; en annan stol och ser <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/see-uhr/</span> sk&auml;lmskt <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/khwelmssth/</span> p&aring; Elsa, som sticker brevet i en bok.)<span class=\"VIiyi\" jsaction=\"mouseup:BR6jm\" jsname=\"jqKxS\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"sv\" data-phrase-index=\"2\" jsaction=\"agoMJf:PFBcW;usxOmf:aWLT7;jhKsnd:P7O7bd,F8DmGf;Q4AGo:Gm7gYd,qAKMYb;uFUCPb:pvnm0e,pfE8Hb,PFBcW;f56efd:dJXsye;EnoYf:KNzws,ZJsZZ,JgVSJc;zdMJQc:cCQNKb,ZJsZZ,zchEXc;Ytrrj:JJDvdc;tNR8yc:GeFvjb;oFN6Ye:hij5Wb\" jscontroller=\"Zl5N8\" jsdata=\"uqLsIf;_;$86\" jsmodel=\"SsMkhd\" jsname=\"txFAF\"><span jsaction=\"click:qtZ4nf,GFf3ac,tMZCfe; contextmenu:Nqw7Te,QP7LD; mouseout:Nqw7Te; mouseover:qtZ4nf,c2aHje\" jsname=\"W297wb\"> <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">[(A farmhouse. Elsa is sitting at the table and reads a letter. Anna comes in, sits down on another chair and looks mischievously at Elsa, who is sticking the letter in a book.)</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">[</span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Sit - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">sitta</span>, Sat - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">satt</span>, Sits - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">sitter</span>, Is sitting - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">sitter</span></li>\n\t<li>Sit down - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">sitt ner</span>, Sat down - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">satt ner</span><span style=\"color:#2c3e50;\">,</span> Sits down - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">s&auml;tter sig ned</span></li>\n\t<li>You sit down - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">du sitter ner,</span>&nbsp; He sat down -&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">han satt ner</span>, He sits down -&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">han s&auml;tter sig</span>, Please sit down - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">sitt ner tack</span></li>\n\t<li>Come in - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">kom in</span>, Came in - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">kom in</span>, Comes in - <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">kommer in</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>]</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold\">Anna</span>. Jas&aring;. Du har f&aring;tt brev fr&aring;n hj&auml;rtev&auml;nnen. &Auml;r det icke s&aring;, Elsa? <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/aerdikesoa/ </span>(Elsa rodnar och sl&aring;r ned &ouml;gonen <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/sloneud-aa&#39;-konen/</span>) . &Aring;h, kors i alla dagar <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/dawgar/</span>, inte beh&ouml;ver <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/baha&#39;ver/</span> du bli chikanerad <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/chike-neyrad/</span> f&ouml;r d&auml; inte <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/for-da&#39;-inte/</span>, som handelsman Blomkvist brukar s&auml;ga <span style=\"color:#f39c12;\">/bruka-se&#39;ya/</span>. <span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\">[<span class=\"VIiyi\" jsaction=\"mouseup:BR6jm\" jsname=\"jqKxS\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"sv\" data-phrase-index=\"0\" jsaction=\"agoMJf:PFBcW;usxOmf:aWLT7;jhKsnd:P7O7bd,F8DmGf;Q4AGo:Gm7gYd,qAKMYb;uFUCPb:pvnm0e,pfE8Hb,PFBcW;f56efd:dJXsye;EnoYf:KNzws,ZJsZZ,JgVSJc;zdMJQc:cCQNKb,ZJsZZ,zchEXc;Ytrrj:JJDvdc;tNR8yc:GeFvjb;oFN6Ye:hij5Wb\" jscontroller=\"Zl5N8\" jsdata=\"uqLsIf;_;$110\" jsmodel=\"SsMkhd\" jsname=\"txFAF\"><span jsaction=\"click:qtZ4nf,GFf3ac,tMZCfe; contextmenu:Nqw7Te,QP7LD; mouseout:Nqw7Te; mouseover:qtZ4nf,c2aHje\" jsname=\"W297wb\">Oh really.</span></span> <span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"sv\" data-phrase-index=\"1\" jsaction=\"agoMJf:PFBcW;usxOmf:aWLT7;jhKsnd:P7O7bd,F8DmGf;Q4AGo:Gm7gYd,qAKMYb;uFUCPb:pvnm0e,pfE8Hb,PFBcW;f56efd:dJXsye;EnoYf:KNzws,ZJsZZ,JgVSJc;zdMJQc:cCQNKb,ZJsZZ,zchEXc;Ytrrj:JJDvdc;tNR8yc:GeFvjb;oFN6Ye:hij5Wb\" jscontroller=\"Zl5N8\" jsdata=\"uqLsIf;_;$111\" jsmodel=\"SsMkhd\" jsname=\"txFAF\"><span jsact